attributes.additional_details:
There is an environmental impact for every product we buy. This is having a detrimental impact on public health, species diversity and climate. In turn this harms crops, economies, living standards/stability. Through eco-labels we will: 
1 Put pressure on manufacturers to adopt more eco-friendly practices; 
2 Empower consumers to make choices which balance personal need with responsibility; 
3 Balance economic prosperity with the environment for the long term benefit of life and planet
